All Classes

  • Class Description
    Asteroid
    Represents asteroids
    AsteroidDestroyer
    Used to mark Participants that destroy Asteroids.
    Asteroids
    The main class for the application.
    Constants
    Provides constants that govern the game.
    Controller
    Controls a game of Asteroids.
    Display
    Defines the top-level appearance of an Asteroids game.
    Participant
    Represents a single moving element in an asteroids game.
    ParticipantCountdownTimer
    Provides objects that wait for a certain amount of time to pass before making a callback to a Participant's countdownComplete method.
    ParticipantState
    Keeps track of the Participants, their motions, and their collisions.
    Screen
    The area of the display in which the game takes place.
    Ship
    Represents ships
    ShipDestroyer
    Used to mark Participants that destroy Ships.
    SoundDemo
    Demonstrates how to put sound files into a project so that they will be included when the project is exported, and demonstrates how to play sounds.
